com.survivingwithandroid.weather.lib
Enum WeatherCode

java.lang.Object
  java.lang.Enum<WeatherCode>
      com.survivingwithandroid.weather.lib.WeatherCode
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<WeatherCode>
public enum WeatherCode
extends java.lang.Enum<WeatherCode>

Unified weather codes. These codes are indipendent from the weather provider used so that a client that wants to use different weather providers at the same time doesn't have to worry about different weather code to implement different custom icons

Author:
Francesco Azzola
See Also:
IWeatherCodeProvider, OpenweathermapCodeProvider, YahooWeatherCodeProvider, WeatherUndergroundCodeProvider
